videos.description: Nicki Ekhomu runs into Kiah Gillespie on the screen, nearly resulting in a Florida State turnover, but Ekhomu recovers and feeds Gillespie, who buries a deep three-pointer.

tracking.trackingName: NCW_One-Play (FSU teammates collide, regroup, then hit deep 3) 2020/3/08 ESHEET

videos.headline: FSU teammates collide, regroup, then hit deep 3

videos.description: NC State's Elissa Cunane swats River Baldwin's shot attempt, then stares down the the Seminoles' freshman center.

tracking.trackingName: NCW_One-Play (Cunane stares down Baldwin after rejection) 2020/3/08 ESHEET

videos.headline: Cunane stares down Baldwin after rejection

videos.description: Aislinn Konig pulls up and knocks down a 3-pointer, capping a 7-0 NC State run.
videos.headline: Konig 3 caps 7-0 Wolfpack run

videos.description: FSU's Kiah Gillespie misses her second free throw and Elissa Cunane loses a shoe as both teams scramble for the loose ball.

tracking.trackingName: NCW_One-Play (Cunane loses shoe in wild loose-ball sequence) 2020/03/08 ESHEET

videos.headline: Cunane loses shoe in wild loose-ball sequence

videos.description: FSU's Nausia Woolfork misses a potential game-tying 3-pointer. Elissa Cunane gets fouled while grabbing the rebound and sinks two free throws to ice the game for NC State.

tracking.trackingName: NCW_One-Play (Cunane’s hustle secures ACC tourney title for NC State) 2020/03/08 ESHEET

videos.headline: Cunane's hustle secures ACC tourney title for NC State
